===Alternative forms===
* [[quote chapter and verse]]

===Etymology===
From the practice, especially among [[Christian]] [[Protestant]]s, of using quotations from the [[Bible]] to support positions taken in sermons or discussions, citing the specific chapter and verse of the books of the Bible.

